"Hello Priti, welcome!  It's a pleasure to meet you.  Thank you for taking the time to interview with us today.  Your resume highlights a strong background in early childhood education, particularly in curriculum development and engaging teaching methods. I'm especially interested in your experience at both Auspicious Beginning and Euro Kids Preschools.

To get started, could you please tell me a little about yourself, your background in education, and what interests you most about this opportunity?"
